### Health
GET http://localhost:8000/health

### Register dev user
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "dev@example.com",
  "password": "replace-with-strong-password",
  "requested_role": "jeweler"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "dev@example.com",
  "password": "replace-with-strong-password"
}

### Current user
GET http://localhost:8000/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer dev-placeholder-token

### Access check
POST http://localhost:8000/access/check
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer dev-placeholder-token

{
  "resource": "workspace"
}

### Plans
GET http://localhost:8000/plans

### Score calculate stub
POST http://localhost:8000/score/calculate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer dev-placeholder-token

{
  "shape": "ROUND",
  "crownAngle": 34.5,
  "pavilionAngle": 40.75,
  "tablePercent": 56,
  "depthPercent": 61.5,
  "language": "RU"
}
